---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About this blog" />
		<style>
			.hero {
				border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));
				background: rgb(238, 240, 244);
				overflow: hidden;
				position: relative;
			}

			.hero-inner {
				width: min(1280px, calc(100% - 2rem));
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 0 2.6rem;
				min-height: 217px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
			}

			.hero-deco {
				position: absolute;
				right: -0.5rem;
				top: 50%;
				transform: translateY(-50%);
				font-size: clamp(7rem, 14vw, 12rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				letter-spacing: -0.04em;
				color: rgba(var(--text), 0.04);
				font-style: italic;
				line-height: 1;
				user-select: none;
				pointer-events: none;
			}

			.crumb {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.82rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				color: rgb(var(--accent));
			}

			.crumb .dim {
				color: rgba(var(--muted), 0.4);
			}

			.hero h1 {
				margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
				display: block;
				width: fit-content;
				position: relative;
			}

			.hero h1::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				left: -4px;
				right: -4px;
				bottom: 0.06em;
				height: 0.36em;
				background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09);
				border-radius: 4px;
			}

			.content {
				max-width: 680px;
				padding-top: 2.4rem;
			}

			.content p {
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: rgba(var(--text), 0.8);
			}

			@media (max-width: 760px) {
				.hero-deco {
					font-size: 6rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<div class="hero">
			<div class="hero-inner">
				<div class="crumb" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dim">~/</span>about</div>
				<h1>About</h1>
			</div>
			<span class="hero-deco" aria-hidden="true">About</span>
		</div>

		<main>
			<div class="content">
				<p>실무 개발에서 얻은 인사이트를 기록하는 개인 기술 블로그입니다.</p>
				<p>아키텍처 의사결정, 마크다운 기반 글쓰기 워크플로, GitHub Pages 운영 패턴을 중심으로 다룹니다.</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
